          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">When can a device alter neural activity without explicit consent? Who owns the data a BCI reads from your cortex? Can an employer require a neural interface? This branch produces the consent models, data sovereignty rules, and access policies that governance enforces.</p>
